80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=5c36d72d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"8114e396956af0034adb114e2a20ecc5bdacf3a2","tid":1042513,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de355358749dbf7f8b80d94366e74487c810f8d6","tid":1042513,"uid":218575,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"我識幾個gaylo 單身緊 <br />\n可介紹俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4083f37a4ad798d1e16bdcbfdd3d66f5657bb7e","tid":1042513,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"做邊行?"},{"pid":"ac36f49da0df3428ad0ec66e5968d95d84b345e5","tid":1042513,"uid":23433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"鳩痕就叫雞啦"},{"pid":"ff81ec6355921980e5aeb237a28f8648e1318982","tid":1042513,"uid":57255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T17:14:22.000Z","msg":"香港係你地頭, 你都識唔到女友<br />\n返大陸搵可能死得仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbc5909f0aa809343911cf23aeaf4111ab2337c","tid":1042513,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79934ee00877b5e8cdb39d301fa3218de4e9e678","tid":1042513,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no